##############   Nested Routing    ########

(1) What is Nested Routing?


    (1)  - NORMAL ROUTING 

     NORMAL ROUTING PATH ->  
        - localhost:3000/about
        - src/about/page.js
     

        (1) Home
        (2) About
        (3) Login
        (4) Profile
        (5) Setting

    (2)  - NESTED ROUTING

     NORMAL ROUTING PATH ->  
        (1) - localhost:3000/aboutcollege
        - src/about/aboutcollege/page.js

        (2) - localhost:3000/aboutstudent
        - src/about/aboutstudent/page.js

        (1) Home
        (2) About - About Student, About College
        (3) Login - Student Login, Teacher Login








